fashion界最紅既都向哂bad blood 個mv到，而且d人都唔係得個紅字，仲係向業界有實力( Kendrick Lamar, Karlie Kloss)。佢搵到個咁既cast同佢拍mv，唔到你唔服。"},{"pid":"b38116513792b1b2ba93de26bd43232f0064ad29","tid":43201,"uid":73534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"Speak now 親筆簽名 賣左未？"},{"pid":"f96147593d911cc6c6a448d5af218c356ba4e4e6","tid":43201,"uid":126014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:53:30.000Z","msg":"結他pick 幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}